* replaced Google+ dummy image with new design

1.2.1 - 2012-01-21

* Fixed a bug that prevented the facebook button from counting properly.
* Merged all CSS in one file.

1.2 - 2011-12-27

* Added option to set custom info URL
* Updated socialshareprivacy jQuery Plugin to new version that supports customizale button captions. (Thanks to Tillmann Kuhn)
* All Graphics are now included in one single sprite. This cuts down network load significally.
* Loading JS in Footer now.

1.1 - 2011-11-16

* Added a helper SocialSharePrivacyHelper that can add Social Buttons to any template though the 
  renderSocialButtons() method
* Fixed a bug where adding of buttons didn't work
* Added block caching support

